      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 text-white">Free Online OCR: Convert Any Image to Text Instantly</h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground mb-8">Need to extract text from a screenshot, scanned PDF, or handwritten note? <strong>OCR (Optical Character Recognition)</strong> technology can do it in seconds. And you don't need to install any software or upload files to sketchy servers.</p>

